  (text "POWER MANAGEMENT\n\nFunction:\n- Buck converter (340V → 15V)\n- LDO regulator (15V → 3.3V)\n- Isolated DC-DC (for sensors)\n- Power sequencing\n- Power good indication\n\nKey Components:\n- LMR51430 buck (4.2-42V, 3A)\n- XC6220B331MR 3.3V LDO (700mA)\n- UCC14240-Q1 isolated DC-DC\n\nPower Rails:\n- +15V: Gate driver, safety logic\n- +3.3V: MCU, digital logic\n- +5V_ISO: Isolated sensors\n\nReference: BOM.md (Power Management section)"
